  "keyFeatures": [
    "Declarative YAML configuration — no CMake scripts or Makefiles required",
    "Profile-based build composition (e.g., debug + asan, release + lto)",
    "Built-in dependency management for Git, vcpkg, local, and system libraries",
    "Reproducible builds with lockfile support via catalyst lock",
    "Workspace support for monorepo multi-package projects",
    "Lifecycle hooks (pre-build, post-build, codegen, etc.) for custom workflows",
    "Multiple build backends: CBE (default), Ninja, GNU Make",
    "Feature flags with preprocessor macro integration",
    "Watch mode for continuous rebuilds on file changes",
    "Cross-compilation support via toolchain profiles"
  ],
